
== SOURCE

https://www.malaymail.com/news/tech-gadgets/2021/09/21/ai-can-now-create-personalised-music/2007358

== AGENT

Malay mail

== GOAL

Generate music in a supposedly "natural" way, based on a theme or a predefined ambiance.

== DATA

The user first selects an ambiance or an emotion, then specifies the type of rhythm and its speed, before finally choosing the duration of the desired loop. The tool then automatically generates musical patterns.

== METHODS

Supervised

== RESULTS

The tool automatically generates musical patterns based on user selection of ambiance, rhythm and speed.

== ISSUES

There is no current issue 

== SCORE

9

== COMMENTS

Playing music with little or no human intervention is impressive, article looks reasonable.
